{
  "ID": "GoR_MinnesotaTribe_DestroyBase_ScorchedData",
  "contractName": "Scorched Data",
  "contractDisplayStyle": "BaseCampaignNormal",
  "difficulty": 7,
  "difficultyUIModifier": 0,
  "weight": 1,
  "scope": "STANDARD",
  "finalDifficulty": 0,
  "shortDescription": "Intelligence reports confirm the presence of <b>Research Station Theta-7</b> on <i>Ryerson</i>, a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} archival facility containing historical records and intelligence assessments related to Clan Wolverine operations. According to our sources, the facility houses classified documentation that could be weaponized against our people if it would become accessible to the Clans.\n\nYour objective is to penetrate the facility's defensive perimeter, eliminate garrison forces, and ensure complete destruction of the data storage infrastructure. Primary targets include the main server vault, backup power systems, and offsite relay nodes. Secondary destruction of physical archives is required to prevent manual recovery.\n\nExpected opposition includes a reinforced garrison lance and automated turret defenses. The facility's remote location provides operational security, but response forces from the regional capital could arrive within hours of alarm activation.\n\nTiming is critical. Complete destruction must be verified before extraction.",
  "longDescription": "Boss, they keep records on people like the Tribe so they can hunt them down if needed. We're making sure those files turn to ash.",
  "salvagePotential": 16,
